## The Eternity Lab Inflection Point

At 2ct total weight, choosing natural over lab for an oval diamond eternity ring costs $124 extra. At 8ct, the same choice costs $23,427. This is the Eternity Lab Inflection Point: the carat weight at which the premium for natural oval eternity bands transitions from a defensible personal preference to a financially irrational one — and where natural also delivers lower clarity than lab.

Rose gold is the only metal with a complete confirmed price series from 2ct through 9.5ct in both natural and lab, enabling an exact comparison at every tier:

