| 7ct | [$25,739](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/oval-cut-eternity-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-7-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-259137?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (-30%) | [$7,640](https://www.bluenile.com/wedding-rings/oval-cut-lab-grown-diamond-eternity-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-7-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-259138?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | $18,099 | 237.0% |
