## Oval Diamond Eternity Bands — White Gold

White gold is the most common metal for oval diamond eternity bands among buyers pairing with a white gold oval engagement ring. 14K white gold receives rhodium plating at manufacture; expect replating every 12–36 months depending on wear frequency and skin chemistry. See the [white gold oval diamond engagement ring guide](/white-gold-oval-diamond-engagement-ring) for the full rhodium renewal schedule.

